            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>808</offset>
                <text>She did not have clinical evidence of Madelung deformity.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>866</offset>
                <text>Radiological imaging revealed shortened metacarpals of her left hand on a bone age X-ray (Figure 2).</text>
                <annotation id="16">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0010049</infon>
                    <location length="21" offset="30"/>
                    <text>shortened metacarpals</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>967</offset>
                <text>She did not have radiological evidence of a Madelung deformity.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1031</offset>
                <text>The mild mesomelia noted clinically was not appreciated on imaging.</text>
                <annotation id="17">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0003027</infon>
